summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Ferdinand Schmitz and Emma Schmitz, his wife, to the City of Seattle, dated the 29th day of January, 1908, to portion of the Northeast quarter NE 1/4 of Northeast quarter (NE 1/4) of Section Fifteen (15), Township twenty-four (24) North, of Range Three (3) East of the Willamette Merdian.
